From building homes to building momentum, SAMANA Developers has redefined growth under our CEO, Mr. Imran Farooq’s leadership. With over 400% sales growth in 2024, a 4.4% market share, and a clear roadmap ahead. We are proud to see him ranked #18 among the Middle East’s Most Influential Construction Leaders of 2025.
